These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, r&b, trance, funk
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of funk is between the fan of r&b and the fan of trance##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| Music-Genre     | rock     | trance | funk  | r&b      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, electrician, videographer, accountant
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the electrician##1
2. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the accountant is on the right of the electrician##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the writer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Job     | writer    | videographer | electrician | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, rowing, cricket
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | rowing   | skateboarding  | cricket |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

