.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, punk, d&b, indie
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the fan of d&b##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | metal   | indie  | d&b |

