.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf, rugby, volleyball
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | golf   | rugby | volleyball    |
| Hobby      | hiking | drawing | singing       | woodworking |

