.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, ice-hockey, climbing
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Sport   | cricket | surfing  | ice-hockey    | climbing  |

