.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, coral, white, pink
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, scientific, superhero
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes pink is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Color         | pink | white | turquise | coral   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific | horror      | superhero |

