.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, horse, snake
There 4 different types of food: pear, pomegranate, cranberry, apple
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating pear##1
2. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
3. the person eating apple is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating pear##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Food   | pomegranate     | cranberry | pear | apple |

