.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, july, november
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Birthday   | july  | june    | april | november |

