.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dannemann, cain, bluemaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the cain-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar       | fonseca | cain | bluemaster    | dannemann      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

