2. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | baking     | chess  | woodworking | hiking |
| Nationality     | egyptian | indonesian | turkish     | nigerian    |

