.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
4 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, backgammon, poker
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
4. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Game           | backgammon     | poker | canasta    | scrabble     |

