.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, daisy, lily
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola    | milk  | fanta |
| Flower   | amaryllis       | balloon-flower | daisy | lily  |

