.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, papaya, plum, pumpkin
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, boat, helicopter, train
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person eating plum##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | pumpkin        | orange       | plum   | papaya |
| Transport    | train | helicopter | boat | motorbike  |

