.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: cherry, apple, carrot, plum
1. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
2. the person eating plum is the person eating plum##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
4. the person eating cherry is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| Food      | cherry | apple | plum | carrot  |

 